Package org.ServerGui.View

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssignPlayerPanel
    Class provides panels containing playerID and possibility to assign player to a specific game.
    AssignPlayerPanelTournament
    Class provides panels containing playerID and possibility to assign player to a specific game.
    GamePanelEndedGame
    Class provides panels containing the game's id, the game's name, possibilty to look up configuration and the winner's name for an ended game.
    GamePanelEndedTournament
    Class provides panels for an ended tournament containing the tournament's id, the tournaments name, the winner's name, possibility to look up the tournament's configuration and possibility to look up the tournament's scorelist.
    GamePanelNotStartedGame
    Class provides panels containing the game's id, the game's name, possibilty to look up configuration and the winner's name for a not started game.
    GamePanelNotStartedTournament
    Class provides panels for a not started tournament containing the tournament's id, the tournaments name, the winner's name, possibility to look up the tournament's configuration and possibility to look up the tournament's scorelist.
    GamePanelStartedGame
    Class provides panels for started games containing the game's id, the game's name, possibilty to look up configuration and the winner's name for a not started game.
    GamePanelStartedTournament
    Class provides panels for a started tournament containing the tournament's id, the tournaments name, the winner's name, possibility to look up the tournament's configuration and possibility to look up the tournament's scorelist.
    GamePanelTournament  
    RankingHeadingPanel
    Class provides panels containing player name, amount of games won and total score in a specific tournament.
    RankingPanel
    Class provides panels containing player name, amount of games won and total score in a specific tournament.
    ScorePanel
    Class provides panels for displaying a player's score.
    SelectWinnerPanel
    Class provides panels for displaying a player's and the possibility to select the player as the winner of an aborted game.
